Sentencas: Planar solid oxide fuel cell technology is being developed at SOFCo in order to demonstrate compact, high-efficiency power-generation systems with multi-fuel capability that can meet commercial performance goals.

Sentencas: Current research focuses on stock development and system integration far pipeline natural gas operation, logistic fuel operation and cell and stock technology for low-temperature operation.
